[{"Id": 1016424, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "Shaheed in his book ''Zikra'' said: Ibn Abi Aqeel has chosen this supplication base on what has been narrated from the commander of the faithful (a) concerning the reappearance of Imam (a) to be recited in Qunoot of Namaz. He said: it gets to me that Imam Sadiq (a) use to command his followers to observe this supplication in their Qunoot after reciting the words of relief (Faraj)…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Shaheed apni kitaab Zikra mein farmate hai: Ibn Abi Aqeel ne is dua ko jo Imam (a) ke zahoor se mutalliq hai usko qunoot ke liye muntakhab kiya hai jo Ameerul Momeneen (a) se waarid huwi hai. Unho ne kaha: mujhe maaloom huwa hai keh Imam Sadiq (a) ne apne maanne waalo’n ko is dua ko dua-e-Faraj ke fauran baad padhne ki taaqid ki hai…", "UrduDescription": "شہید اول کتاب ذکری میں فرماتے ہیں ابن ابی عقیل نے قنوت کے لئے جو دعائیں امیر المومنین سے روایت کی ہیں وہ دعا یہ ہے۔ اسی طرح فرماتے ہیں میرے لئے نقل ہوا ہے کہ امام صادق نے اپنے شیعوں کو حکم دیا کہ قنوت میں کلمات فرج کے بعد اس دُعا کو پڑھیں۔۔۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "