ull, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1016425, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O Allah! All sight ascend to You and feet convey to You, the hands are raised to You, the necks are extended to You, He who was called by tongues, You attain peoples secrets and confidential talks in their action. O our Lord! Initiate the path of fact between us and our people, You are the best initiator.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "INSHA-ALLAH COMING SOON", "Urdu": "انشاء اللہ ترجمہ جلد آرہا ہے", "RArabic": "ALLAAHUMMA ILAIY-KA SHA-KHASA-TIL AB-SAARO, WA NOQE-LA-TUL AQ-DAAMO, WA ROFE-A’TIL AIY-DEE, WA MUDDA-TIL A’NAA-QO, WA ANTA DO-EE’TO BIL-AL-SONE, WA ILAIY-KA SIRRO-HUM WA NAJWAA-HUM FIL A’MAA-LE, RABBA-NAF-TAH BAIY-NA-NAA WA BAIY-NA QAWME-NAA BIL-HAQQE WA ANTA KHAI-RUL FAATE-HEENA.", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰھُمَّ اِلَیْكَ شَخَصَتِ الْاَبْصَارُ، وَنُقِلَتُ الْاَقْدَامُ، وَرُفِعَتِ الْاَیْدِیْ، وَمُدَّتِ الْاَعْنَاقُ، وَاَنْتَ دُعِیْتُ بِالْاَلْسُنِ، وَاِلَیْكَ سِرُّهُمْ وَنَجْوَاهُمْ فِی الْاَعْمَالِ، رَبَّنَا افْتَحْ بَیْنَنَا وَبَیْنَ قَوْمِنَا بِالْحَقِّ وَاَنْتَ خَیْرُ الْفَاتِحِیْنَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1016426, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O Allah! We complain the absence of our Prophet to you and the littleness of our number and the abundance of our enemy and the pretenses of our enemy on us and occurrence of afflictions on us, O Allah! Relief us with Your manifested justice and introduce the trusted Imam to us, O Allah the Lord of the worlds. Aameen!", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": "ALLAAHUMMA INNAA NASH-KOO ILAIY-KA GHAI-BA-TA NABIYYE-NAA WA QILLA-TA A’DA-DE-NAA, WA KASRA-TA A’DOOWE-NAA, WA TAZAAHO-RAL A’DAAA-E A’LAIY-NAA, WA WOQOO-A’L FETA-NE-BENAA, FA-FARRIJ ZAALE-KAL-LAAHUMMA BE-A’DLIN TUZHE-ROHU, WA IMAAME HAQQE TO-A’RRE-FOHU, ILAA-HAL HAQQE AA-MEENA RABBAL A’ALA-MEENA.", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ اِنَّا نَشْكُوْ اِلَیْكَ غَیْبَۃَ نَبِیِّنَا وَقِلَّۃَ عَدَدِنَا، وَكَثْرَۃَ عَدُوِّنَا، وَتَظَاهُرَ الْاَعْدَاۗئِ عَلَیْنَا، وَوُقُوْعَ الْفِتَنِ بِنَا، فَفَرِّجْ ذٰلِكَ اللّٰهُمَّ بِعَدْلٍ تُظْهِرُهٗ، وَاِمَامِ حَقٍّ تُعَرِّفُهٗ، اِلٰهَ الْحَقِّ اٰمِیْنَ رَبَ الْعَالَمِیْنَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null,